node.title: Carnarvon man Terence Darrell Kelly charged with abducting Cleo Smith
node.description: The 36-year-old man has been charged over the abduction ofÂ four-year-old Cleo Smith during a family camping trip.
node.content: ["Police have charged a Western Australian man over the abduction\u00a0of four-year-old Cleo Smith.", "Cleo was found in the bedroom of a locked house in the northern WA town of Carnarvon in the early hours of Wednesday morning, 18 days after her family reported her missing.", "Police have been questioning Terence Darrell Kelly, 36, for the past two days and have this afternoon\u00a0charged him with two offences, including abducting Cleo.", "Mr Kelly was arrested on a street in town after\u00a0police officers broke into the state housing commission home he was living in and found Cleo\u00a0playing with toys inside.", "It's alleged he took the four-year-old while she slept inside her family's tent at the Blowholes Campground\u00a0on October 16.", "Her disappearance sparked a massive\u00a0police search.", "More to come."]
